## Đọc Theo Workflow

### Autonomy Path A (Bug Fix):
```
CORE_ROLE → 90_mcp_and_git.mdc → logs.txt → root cause → fix
```

### Autonomy Path B (Vague):
```
CORE_ROLE → memory-bank/* → hỏi user
```

### Autonomy Path C (Well-Defined):
```
CORE_ROLE → this file → Xác định files cần đọc → tasks/todo.md
```

### /ag/plan (Tech Vision - Plugin):
```
CORE_ROLE → .claude/plugins/plan-workflow/workflows/tech_vision.md
→ Đọc memory-bank → User provides idea
→ AI analyzes & expands → Ask decisions
→ Detect conflicts → Generate tech vision
→ Auto-update memory-bank
```

**Plugin:** plan-workflow v1.0.0
**Output:** `memory-bank/tech-vision/[name].md`

### /ag/setupplan (Screen Planning - Plugin):
```
CORE_ROLE → .claude/plugins/plan-workflow/workflows/setup_plan.md
→ Đọc 6 memory-bank + DB Schema
→ DB Analysis + Logic Analysis
→ Design System Sync + UI Template Transformer
→ Cross-Reference + Generate Spec
→ Update memory-bank
```

**Plugin:** plan-workflow v1.0.0
**Features:** DB Analysis, Logic Analysis, Design Sync, UI Transformer
**Output:** `memory-bank/plan/[screen].md` + `lib/widgets/generated/`

